issue.name: Strict transport security not enforced
issue.description: This issue was found in multiple locations under the reported path.

issue.name: Mixed content
issue.description:
The response is loaded over HTTPS, but loads other resources over an unencrypted connection. The following "active" resource is loaded over HTTP. An attacker able to modify traffic could cause execution of arbitrary script within the user's browser:
  • http://public-firing-range.appspot.com/mixedcontent/script.js
issue.caption: /mixedcontent/index.html

issue.name: Private IP addresses disclosed
issue.description:
The following RFC 1918 IP address was disclosed in the response:
  • 192.168.1.2
issue.caption: /badscriptimport/index.html
